00:05:15.800 --> 00:05:16.630
isn't it already

00:05:16.630 --> 00:05:17.560
quite clear now?

00:05:18.650 --> 00:05:19.630
Since we have Yu Qifeng,

00:05:19.630 --> 00:05:21.030
a more significant lead,

00:05:21.360 --> 00:05:23.560
