00:06:20.640 --> 00:06:22.370
would lead to a series of cases.

00:06:23.190 --> 00:06:24.720
If it weren't for your help,

00:06:25.430 --> 00:06:27.040
I wouldn't have been able to uncover

00:06:27.040 --> 00:06:29.040
the Fengliu Shop as the mastermind.

00:06:29.040 --> 00:06:29.920
I didn't really

00:06:29.920 --> 00:06:31.650
intend to help you, Miss Zhong.

00:06:31.990 --> 00:06:33.720
Rather, I used you

00:06:34.430 --> 00:06:35.960
to accomplish my own goals.

00:06:37.000 --> 00:06:39.310
