00:07:07.800 --> 00:07:09.610
Sword King City has
thousands of disciples.

00:07:09.610 --> 00:07:11.500
Yu Qifeng has the title of Sword King.

00:07:11.500 --> 00:07:12.650
The likes of Yang Shangqing

00:07:12.650 --> 00:07:14.850
or Jiang Qingyu can't compare with him.

00:07:14.950 --> 00:07:16.350
If he's really involved,

00:07:16.750 --> 00:07:17.430
then Sword King City

00:07:17.430 --> 00:07:19.360
is undoubtedly a dangerous place.

00:07:23.560 --> 00:07:25.270
Why not wait until I report to my master

00:07:25.270 --> 00:07:26.730
and people from the Sword Alliance?

00:07:26.730 --> 00:07:27.560
When the time comesâ€”

