I've already made it clear.

00:07:31.870 --> 00:07:32.510
I am

00:07:33.000 --> 00:07:35.230
not trying to help
the Sword Alliance solve cases,

00:07:35.230 --> 00:07:36.230
nor do I care about

00:07:36.510 --> 00:07:37.480
whether the Blood Ghost Pill

00:07:37.480 --> 00:07:39.340
poses a threat to the world or not.

00:07:39.760 --> 00:07:41.000
