00:10:59.200 --> 00:11:00.460
so the people behind it

00:11:00.620 --> 00:11:02.080
will have nowhere to hide.

00:11:03.960 --> 00:11:06.000
That's what I'm here for.

00:11:06.480 --> 00:11:08.390
If you say you can make Yu Qifeng

00:11:08.390 --> 00:11:10.720
so angry he vomits blood, I'll believe it.

00:11:10.870 --> 00:11:11.930
But when it comes to

00:11:12.120 --> 00:11:14.550
lurking in the shadows and finding clues,

00:11:15.820 --> 00:11:17.110
