Whether it's you or him,

00:19:37.360 --> 00:19:38.430
it's all the same.

00:19:41.850 --> 00:19:43.090
Shadow Concealment Technique?

00:19:43.090 --> 00:19:45.350
Every grievance and debt has its source.

00:19:45.350 --> 00:19:47.480
You've always been a sensible person.

00:19:48.350 --> 00:19:50.000
The Shisan Tower once,
on behalf of this person,

00:19:50.000 --> 00:19:51.610
delivered a flute to me.

00:19:51.850 --> 00:19:53.310
He only asked you to run an errand

00:19:53.310 --> 00:19:54.370
but didn't tell you

00:19:54.400 --> 00:19:56.530
the story behind this half jade flute.

00:19:56.760 --> 00:19:58.160
It seems that you, Chief,

00:19:58.480 --> 00:20:00.030
are also one of his pawns.

00:20:05.110 --> 00:20:06.110
Mr. Tang,

00:20:07.100 --> 00:20:08.380
four years ago,

00:20:08.730 --> 00:20:09.930
you died.

00:20:13.270 --> 00:20:13.920
So what?

00:20:15.000 --> 00:20:16.930
A broken flute cannot be rejoined,

00:20:17.030 --> 00:20:19.160
yet a dead person can come back to life.

00:20:19.240 --> 00:20:20.640
I'm very curious

00:20:20.920 --> 00:20:22.580
about the secret behind this.

00:20:23.240 --> 00:20:25.310
Chief, your curiosity

00:20:26.030 --> 00:20:27.750
won't help you do business.

00:20:33.830 --> 00:20:35.630
Since you're here for business,

00:20:35.680 --> 00:20:36.610
what do you seek?

00:20:37.110 --> 00:20:38.770
You have eyes and ears everywhere.

00:20:38.770 --> 00:20:40.030
You must already know

00:20:40.030 --> 00:20:41.070
why I'm here.

00:20:42.030 --> 00:20:43.200
Today, I've come

00:20:43.550 --> 00:20:45.200
to request the services
of Shisan Tower's top assassin,

00:20:45.200 --> 00:20:46.200
Shen Langhun,

00:20:46.640 --> 00:20:47.750
for one year.

00:20:49.640 --> 00:20:51.070
This isn't your first time

00:20:51.070 --> 00:20:53.200
doing business with the Shisan Tower.

00:20:53.200 --> 00:20:54.880
You should know our rules.

00:20:57.590 --> 00:20:59.550
I don't make a habit of buying on credit.

00:20:59.550 --> 00:21:00.880
Please name your price.

00:21:05.820 --> 00:21:07.480
Foxy Tang, be careful.

00:21:08.040 --> 00:21:09.510
He's utterly ruthless.

00:21:10.960 --> 00:21:12.440
What if what I want

00:21:12.650 --> 00:21:13.610
is you?

00:21:16.980 --> 00:21:18.380
That would be difficult.

00:21:18.860 --> 00:21:19.680
I consider myself

00:21:19.680 --> 00:21:21.540
more valuable than Shen Langhun.

00:21:21.890 --> 00:21:23.560
Perhaps you could pay the difference?

00:21:23.560 --> 00:21:24.470
What a pity.

00:21:25.310 --> 00:21:28.000
I'm interested, but you are not.

00:21:29.200 --> 00:21:30.730
If you want Shen Langhun...

00:21:32.920 --> 00:21:35.720
you'll have to come upstairs
to find him yourself.

00:21:58.810 --> 00:22:00.050
Go! I'll cover you.

00:22:47.000 --> 00:22:48.800
Shadow Concealment Technique?

00:22:48.900 --> 00:22:50.560
Chi Yun, you've grown taller.

00:22:50.860 --> 00:22:51.290
What?

00:22:53.320 --> 00:22:54.520
What the hell is that?

00:22:55.440 --> 00:22:56.040
Foxy Tang,

00:22:56.310 --> 00:22:57.640
can you speak properly?

00:22:58.150 --> 00:22:58.980
Mr. Tang,

00:22:59.440 --> 00:23:01.000
four years ago, Liu Yan slit your throat

00:23:01.000 --> 00:23:02.400
and threw you into a well.

00:23:02.480 --> 00:23:04.000
No one could survive

00:23:04.000 --> 00:23:05.330
in such circumstances.

00:23:06.640 --> 00:23:07.640
But now,

00:23:07.640 --> 00:23:08.640
you're not only alive

00:23:08.640 --> 00:23:09.830
and standing here,

00:23:10.270 --> 00:23:11.590
but also stirring up

00:23:11.880 --> 00:23:13.740
tremendous waves in the jianghu.

00:24:17.740 --> 00:24:18.740
Mr. Tang,

00:24:19.280 --> 00:24:20.740
is your secret of not dying

00:24:20.780 --> 00:24:22.540
derived from your body

00:24:22.720 --> 00:24:24.880
or from the martial arts you practice?

00:24:31.000 --> 00:24:33.050
Chief, your life
is already hanging by a thread.

00:24:33.050 --> 00:24:34.810
Why bother asking about things

00:24:35.200 --> 00:24:36.530
that don't concern you?

00:24:39.110 --> 00:24:39.750
Is that so?

00:24:40.240 --> 00:24:41.070
But what if

00:24:41.070 --> 00:24:42.800
I insist on knowing the answer?

00:24:44.350 --> 00:24:45.590
You should know

00:24:45.810 --> 00:24:48.340
that the more you know,
the faster you'll die.

00:25:02.230 --> 00:25:03.890
Is this all you're capable of?

00:25:04.000 --> 00:25:05.240
With such limited skills,

00:25:05.240 --> 00:25:06.990
you're not worthy of hearing my secrets.

00:25:06.990 --> 00:25:09.450
I built this tower
with all my heart and soul.

00:25:09.920 --> 00:25:11.920
You haven't seen even half of it yet.

00:25:46.740 --> 00:25:47.560
Die!

00:26:01.750 --> 00:26:02.880
Gui Fusheng?

00:26:05.480 --> 00:26:06.210
Take it back.

00:26:40.200 --> 00:26:42.230
Turns out the mechanisms
of the Fallen Shisan Tower

00:26:42.230 --> 00:26:44.790
were created
by the world's greatest puppet master,

00:26:44.790 --> 00:26:45.960
Gui Fusheng.

00:26:55.750 --> 00:26:56.710
Mr. Tang.

00:26:57.370 --> 00:26:59.270
You think just because you won't talk,

00:26:59.270 --> 00:27:00.960
the Shisan Tower won't find out

00:27:00.960 --> 00:27:02.020
about your secret?

00:27:03.070 --> 00:27:04.020
Do you know

00:27:04.720 --> 00:27:06.200
that before the Shisan Tower,

00:27:06.200 --> 00:27:08.440
no secret can remain hidden?

00:27:25.480 --> 00:27:26.520
Foxy Tang!

00:28:17.880 --> 00:28:18.830
Mr. Tang,

00:28:19.140 --> 00:28:21.060
your martial arts skills
are indeed impressive,

00:28:21.060 --> 00:28:21.720
but I

00:28:21.720 --> 00:28:23.680
have yet to witness that one move

00:28:24.070 --> 00:28:25.240
I've been longing to see.

00:28:25.240 --> 00:28:26.900
Why must you be so persistent?

00:28:26.990 --> 00:28:28.380
All will be seen from the tower.

00:28:28.380 --> 00:28:29.840
Where is the person I want?

00:28:31.680 --> 00:28:32.480
Mr. Tang,

00:28:32.960 --> 00:28:34.480
being stubborn is wrong,

00:28:35.200 --> 00:28:36.920
but so is

00:28:37.160 --> 00:28:38.270
being arrogant.

00:29:11.820 --> 00:29:13.020
You're finally here,

00:29:13.510 --> 00:29:14.680
Shen Langhun

00:29:17.390 --> 00:29:18.850
Mr. Tang, when you strike,

00:29:19.030 --> 00:29:20.480
you always turn sideways.

00:29:20.480 --> 00:29:22.000
When turning,

00:29:22.050 --> 00:29:24.310
your energy flow is clearly obstructed.

00:29:24.560 --> 00:29:27.640
You have an old wound in your abdomen

00:29:27.660 --> 00:29:28.920
that cannot be healed.

00:29:29.670 --> 00:29:31.160
Am I right?

00:29:34.780 --> 00:29:36.060
You've hidden it well,

00:29:36.200 --> 00:29:37.710
but I have still

00:29:37.740 --> 00:29:39.200
managed to see through it.

00:29:41.590 --> 00:29:42.640
Back in the day,

00:29:42.660 --> 00:29:45.520
seven great masters fought against
Yique Yinyang.

00:29:45.550 --> 00:29:47.810
Fang Zhou deserved the greatest credit.

00:29:48.110 --> 00:29:49.170
After that battle,

00:29:49.270 --> 00:29:52.240
he was honored as the world's greatest.

00:29:53.200 --> 00:29:54.310
Tang Lici,

00:29:54.800 --> 00:29:56.240
could your abdomen wound

00:29:57.050 --> 00:29:59.440
be from Fang Zhou?

00:30:07.370 --> 00:30:08.200
Shen Langhun,

00:30:08.450 --> 00:30:09.780
attack his old wound.

00:30:57.070 --> 00:30:57.960
Snake Fang...

00:30:59.480 --> 00:31:00.440
Soul Breaker!

00:31:12.750 --> 00:31:13.640
Got him.

00:32:09.440 --> 00:32:10.070
This is...

00:32:14.270 --> 00:32:16.070
Since you insisted on seeing it,

00:32:16.440 --> 00:32:17.330
then

00:32:17.840 --> 00:32:19.120
watch this carefully.

00:32:36.600 --> 00:32:37.600
I understand now.

00:32:38.160 --> 00:32:39.160
I understand now!

00:32:39.680 --> 00:32:40.880
You're just like him.

00:32:43.240 --> 00:32:45.270
The infinite secrets of human and man,

00:32:45.270 --> 00:32:47.400
the Liuli Rebirth Scroll.

00:32:48.150 --> 00:32:49.480
Only the Rebirth Scroll

00:32:50.030 --> 00:32:52.750
can continuously transform
and sustain life,

00:32:53.040 --> 00:32:55.400
allowing you
to recover from severe injuries

00:32:55.400 --> 00:32:56.790
and come back to life.

00:32:58.400 --> 00:32:59.350
But why?

00:33:01.200 --> 00:33:02.070
But why

00:33:02.070 --> 00:33:04.600
do you possess
Yique Yinyang's martial arts?

00:33:05.740 --> 00:33:06.430
And also,

00:33:07.160 --> 00:33:08.620
that wound on your abdomen

00:33:08.920 --> 00:33:09.920
that even the Rebirth Scroll

00:33:09.920 --> 00:33:11.640
cannot heal...

00:33:13.790 --> 00:33:15.980
What exactly is it?

00:33:17.990 --> 00:33:20.590
If you want to
peek into the darkness of one's heart,

00:33:20.590 --> 00:33:23.790
be careful not to get dragged into
the darkness yourself.

00:33:25.280 --> 00:33:26.440
Tang Lici,

00:33:27.190 --> 00:33:29.190
you amuse me greatly.

00:33:34.500 --> 00:33:36.230
You can take Shen Langhun away,

00:33:36.480 --> 00:33:38.370
but whether he'll obey you

00:33:39.110 --> 00:33:40.830
depends on your ability.

00:33:43.250 --> 00:33:44.750
Isn't it just a fair exchange of

00:33:44.750 --> 00:33:46.080
paying money for a life?

00:33:47.790 --> 00:33:48.830
Since when did the Shisan Tower

00:33:48.830 --> 00:33:50.200
add this new rule?

00:33:51.110 --> 00:33:52.110
That has never been

00:33:52.110 --> 00:33:54.110
the rule of the Fallen Shisan Tower.

00:33:55.310 --> 00:33:57.170
It was established four years ago

00:33:57.750 --> 00:34:00.640
by Shen Langhun himself.

00:34:36.440 --> 00:34:37.110
Sword King,

00:34:38.090 --> 00:34:39.380
you finally came.

00:34:40.960 --> 00:34:43.090
If you hadn't personally intervened,

00:34:43.179 --> 00:34:43.880
I would certainly

00:34:43.880 --> 00:34:44.920
have been taken away by

00:34:44.920 --> 00:34:47.710
that little girl
from the Central Plains Sword Alliance.

00:34:47.710 --> 00:34:49.570
I won't ask you for anything more.

00:34:50.170 --> 00:34:52.150
I only ask that you allow me
to leave the city.

00:34:52.150 --> 00:34:53.679
Let me go to the countryside

00:34:53.870 --> 00:34:56.020
and live as an ordinary villager.

00:35:00.840 --> 00:35:01.510
Sword King!

00:35:02.720 --> 00:35:04.030
Sword King, rest assured.

00:35:04.030 --> 00:35:05.290
I'm very tight-lipped

00:35:05.450 --> 00:35:07.340
and won't implicate the Sword King City.

00:35:07.340 --> 00:35:08.900
About you selling me the medicine,

00:35:08.900 --> 00:35:11.300
I haven't mentioned
a single word about it.

00:35:26.070 --> 00:35:27.320
Who did you say

00:35:29.930 --> 00:35:31.190
sold you the medicine?

00:35:57.470 --> 00:35:58.800
The Sword King is tired.

00:35:58.960 --> 00:36:00.630
I need to help him relax.

00:36:01.130 --> 00:36:02.170
Clean up

00:36:02.460 --> 00:36:03.190
and leave us.

00:36:03.830 --> 00:36:05.310
Yes, Madam Bai.

00:36:21.150 --> 00:36:22.230
What you just did

00:36:22.850 --> 00:36:23.930
was not wise.

00:36:24.670 --> 00:36:27.360
This matter could have been
handled more elegantly.

00:36:27.360 --> 00:36:28.760
The suspect Jiang Qingyu

00:36:29.110 --> 00:36:31.510
feared revenge
from the Fengliu Shop's inhuman forces

00:36:31.510 --> 00:36:33.110
and committed suicide out of guilt.

00:36:33.110 --> 00:36:35.000
But your impulsive strike

00:36:35.630 --> 00:36:37.760
has needlessly cut off this approach.

00:36:38.670 --> 00:36:39.730
I am the Sword King.

00:36:40.280 --> 00:36:42.000
Why bother with such deception?

00:36:42.000 --> 00:36:43.590
If I say
he committed suicide out of guilt,

00:36:43.590 --> 00:36:45.120
then that's what happened.

00:36:45.760 --> 00:36:47.160
Who dares to question it?

00:36:47.190 --> 00:36:48.510
You are so bold.

00:36:48.710 --> 00:36:49.590
It seems Fengliu Shop

00:36:49.590 --> 00:36:51.150
sending me to assist the Sword King

00:36:51.150 --> 00:36:52.550
was unnecessary.

00:36:53.520 --> 00:36:54.960
I hope in a few days

00:36:55.030 --> 00:36:57.340
when questioned by
the Central Plains Sword Alliance,

00:36:57.340 --> 00:36:59.220
you will show the same courage.

00:36:59.550 --> 00:37:01.080
Master, you worry too much.

00:37:01.300 --> 00:37:03.360
Those incompetent and ignorant elders

00:37:03.360 --> 00:37:04.510
can do nothing to me.

00:37:05.480 --> 00:37:06.760
What about Tang Lici,

00:37:06.880 --> 00:37:08.110
the one at Yanmen Fort who withstood

00:37:08.110 --> 00:37:09.150
your strike?

00:37:21.840 --> 00:37:23.730
[Central Plains Sword Alliance]

00:37:25.880 --> 00:37:27.140
That's what happened.

00:37:27.470 --> 00:37:28.130
After that,

00:37:28.160 --> 00:37:29.890
Sword King Yu left with the man.

00:37:30.070 --> 00:37:30.840
I believe

00:37:31.200 --> 00:37:32.850
the case of the Blood Ghost Pill

00:37:32.850 --> 00:37:34.910
must be connected to Sword King City.

00:37:34.950 --> 00:37:37.280
Please investigate thoroughly, Master.

00:37:38.190 --> 00:37:39.070
Nonsense!

00:37:39.410 --> 00:37:40.480
Do you know

00:37:40.480 --> 00:37:41.610
who Sword King Yu is?

00:37:42.000 --> 00:37:43.730
Since the Yu family's ancestors

00:37:43.730 --> 00:37:45.790
founded Phoenix Manor 300 years ago,

00:37:45.920 --> 00:37:48.120
10 generations of renowned Sword Kings

00:37:48.230 --> 00:37:50.320
have had the reputation
of Sword Grandmaster.

00:37:50.320 --> 00:37:52.070
Moreover, Yu Xuanqing the Sword Phoenix

00:37:52.070 --> 00:37:53.360
had joined Head Fang and other masters

00:37:53.360 --> 00:37:54.880
10 years ago at Tiandu Peak,

00:37:54.880 --> 00:37:57.080
and jointly eliminated Yique Yinyang.

00:37:57.320 --> 00:37:59.250
He's truly an exemplar of our time.

00:37:59.640 --> 00:38:01.600
Now, you dare accuse Sword King Yu

00:38:02.010 --> 00:38:03.230
of colluding with Fengliu Shop

00:38:03.230 --> 00:38:05.150
to sell Blood Ghost Pills?

00:38:05.830 --> 00:38:06.960
Sword Master Jiang,

00:38:07.410 --> 00:38:09.210
Jiang Qingyu was just captured,

00:38:09.550 --> 00:38:11.590
and Sword King Yu arrived right after.

00:38:11.590 --> 00:38:13.400
How could he have such timely information?

00:38:13.400 --> 00:38:15.130
If you want to suspect someone,

00:38:15.280 --> 00:38:17.440
you should first suspect Tang Lici.

00:38:18.040 --> 00:38:19.360
You said the black-clad pipa player

00:38:19.360 --> 00:38:21.160
disguised himself as Tang Lici,

00:38:21.210 --> 00:38:22.440
intending to bring up

00:38:22.500 --> 00:38:24.160
the unsolved case of Zhoudi Tower.

00:38:24.160 --> 00:38:25.690
But have you all considered

00:38:26.000 --> 00:38:27.590
that if the black-clad pipa player

00:38:27.590 --> 00:38:29.590
had no real connection,

00:38:30.030 --> 00:38:32.070
how could he stir up so much trouble?

00:38:32.280 --> 00:38:33.280
Now, someone has finally

00:38:33.280 --> 00:38:34.710
delivered a clue to our doorstep.

00:38:34.710 --> 00:38:36.060
Instead of tracking him down

00:38:36.060 --> 00:38:37.990
to investigate Head Fang's death,

00:38:38.320 --> 00:38:40.050
you're letting him lead you on.

00:38:40.920 --> 00:38:41.670
That's right.

00:38:41.670 --> 00:38:43.150
This person hid for four years.

00:38:43.150 --> 00:38:44.000
As soon as he appeared,

00:38:44.000 --> 00:38:45.360
he caused so much trouble.

00:38:45.360 --> 00:38:46.880
The Ranqing Sect was massacred.

00:38:46.880 --> 00:38:47.840
Some people say

00:38:48.000 --> 00:38:49.880
Tang Lici is the real culprit
behind it all.

00:38:49.880 --> 00:38:51.140
He was clearly framed.

00:38:51.400 --> 00:38:52.070
You should know

00:38:52.070 --> 00:38:53.800
that when
the Ranqing Sect incident happened,

00:38:53.800 --> 00:38:55.710
Tang Lici and I
were both at Yanmen Fort.

00:38:55.710 --> 00:38:56.550
Their attempt to use the same trick

00:38:56.550 --> 00:38:57.280
is so clumsy.

00:38:57.800 --> 00:38:59.400
Can't you all see through it?

00:38:59.670 --> 00:39:00.530
You should know

00:39:00.550 --> 00:39:01.710
the one who massacred

00:39:01.710 --> 00:39:02.960
the Ranqing Sect was a woman in red.

00:39:02.960 --> 00:39:04.360
When you were at Yanmen Fort,

00:39:04.360 --> 00:39:05.440
did you see her?

00:39:06.230 --> 00:39:07.550
If Tang Lici wanted to do evil,

00:39:07.550 --> 00:39:09.230
why would he need to act personally?

00:39:09.230 --> 00:39:10.630
Perhaps that black-clad pipa player

00:39:10.630 --> 00:39:11.960
is also his accomplice.

00:39:12.530 --> 00:39:14.560
Chunji, your experience in the jianghu
is still limited.

00:39:14.560 --> 00:39:17.420
You may know someone's surface
but not their heart.

00:39:20.840 --> 00:39:22.110
Sword King Yu ignored the Sword Alliance

00:39:22.110 --> 00:39:23.310
and took the man away,

00:39:23.440 --> 00:39:25.920
yet the Sword Alliance
only questions Tang Lici.

00:39:25.920 --> 00:39:27.440
When it comes to Sword King Yu,

00:39:27.440 --> 00:39:29.440
don't you even dare to question him?

00:39:29.510 --> 00:39:31.370
Since the Sword Alliance bullies the weak
and fears the strong,

00:39:31.370 --> 00:39:32.610
if I handed the person over to Yu Qifeng,

00:39:32.610 --> 00:39:34.340
wouldn't I be doing you a favor?

00:39:34.550 --> 00:39:35.550
You've just become

00:39:35.550 --> 00:39:36.550
the Branch Chief of Shanfeng Branch.

00:39:36.550 --> 00:39:37.840
Have you already disregarded

00:39:37.840 --> 00:39:38.760
the Sword Alliance

00:39:38.760 --> 00:39:40.000
and us Sword Masters?

00:39:41.400 --> 00:39:43.510
For an outsider like Tang Lici,

00:39:44.150 --> 00:39:46.010
you're actually arguing with us.

00:39:46.510 --> 00:39:47.880
I've said it before.

00:39:48.180 --> 00:39:50.310
She's too young and incompetent.

00:39:51.000 --> 00:39:52.710
Coming from the lowest class,

00:39:53.470 --> 00:39:54.930
she's also shortsighted.

00:39:57.910 --> 00:39:59.110
Second Sword Master,

00:39:59.480 --> 00:40:00.110
why make it about

00:40:00.110 --> 00:40:02.170
the Third Sword Master for no reason?

00:40:02.180 --> 00:40:03.560
She used to be a butcher.

00:40:04.070 --> 00:40:04.840
What's it to you?

00:40:04.840 --> 00:40:06.190
I never said that.

00:40:06.630 --> 00:40:07.880
When you were scolding Chunji,

00:40:07.880 --> 00:40:09.270
you should have just stated the issue.

00:40:09.270 --> 00:40:10.330
Why call her lowly?

00:40:13.270 --> 00:40:13.880
Everyone,

00:40:14.070 --> 00:40:15.760
don't embarrass ourselves
before the younger generation.

00:40:15.760 --> 00:40:17.720
The Sword King
is also a member of the Sword Alliance.

00:40:17.720 --> 00:40:19.250
The trial of the Yanmen case

00:40:19.490 --> 00:40:21.020
is perfectly appropriate.

